

# 1  GoCloud SDK 测试

## 1.1  ExtendedSQL 查询

POST请求URL: `http://{{ip}}:{{port}}/goinsight/execute`

Text类型的请求体:

```json
{
	"requestHeader": {
		"serviceType": 2,
		"moduleType": 7,
		"requestType": 3
	},
	"request": {
		"natived": "TB_WIFI_TERMINAL_INFO/select?q=IsEnter:0&rows=0&start=0&wt=json&indent=true"
	}
}
```

# 3  GoSearch 请求

## 3.1  ES 请求

### 3.1.1  ES 通过其 URL 请求

POST请求URL: `172.16.22.131:9200/your_index/_search`

JSON类型的请求体:

```json
{
  "query": {
    "match_all": {}
  },
  "from": 10,
  "size": 2
}
```

### 3.1.2  ES 单机

POST请求URL: `http://{{ip}}:{{port}}/goSearch/query.htm`

JSON类型的请求体:

```json
{
	"requestHeader": {
		"serviceType": 2,
		"moduleType": 8,
		"requestType": 3
	}, 
	"request": {
		"natived": {
			"index": "test",
			"query": {
				"query": {
					"match_all": {}
				},
				"from": 2,
				"size": 2
			}
		}
	}
}
```

### 3.1.2  ES 集群

POST请求URL: `http://{{ip}}:{{port}}/goSearch/query.htm`

JSON类型的请求体:

```json
{
	"requestHeader": {
		"serviceType": 2,
		"moduleType": 8,
		"requestType": 3
	}, 
	"request": {
		"natived": {
			"index": "tb_face",
			"condition": {
				"_source": {
					"includes": ["InfoKind", "Similaritydegree", "ShotTime", "IDNumber", "Name"]
				},
				"query": {
					"match_phrase": {
						"ShotTime": "2018-12-08 00:06:11"
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}
}
```



## 3.2  Solr 请求

### 3.2.1  natived 请求

POST请求URL: `http://{{ip}}:{{port}}/goSearch/query.htm`

JSON类型的请求体:

```json
{
	"requestHeader": {
		"serviceType": 2,
		"moduleType": 7,
		"requestType": 3
	},
	"request": {
		"natived": "TB_WIFI_TERMINAL_INFO/select?q=IsEnter:0&rows=1&start=2&wt=json&indent=true"
	}
}
```

### 3.2.2  extendedSQL 查询请求

POST请求URL: `http://{{ip}}:{{port}}/goSearch/query.htm`

JSON类型的请求体:

```json
{
	"requestHeader": {
		"serviceType": 2,
		"moduleType": 7,
		"requestType": 2
	},
	"request": {
		"extendedSql": {
			"facet": "facet.query=NetbarWacode: XXX08*&facet.field=Brand",
			"sql": "select * from TB_WIFI_TERMINAL_INFO limit 0, 1"
		}
	}
}
```

### 3.2.3  extendedSQL 添加请求

POST请求URL: `http://{{ip}}:{{port}}/goSearch/query.htm`

JSON类型的请求体:

```json
{
	"requestHeader": {
		"serviceType": 2,
		"moduleType": 7,
		"requestType": 2
	},
	"request": {
		"extendedSql": {
			"sql": "insert into TB_WIFI_TERMINAL_INFO (TerminalID,Brand,IsEnter) values('101','华为','1')"
		}
	}
}
```



## 3.3  赤峰-车辆属性统计

其中“property”有6种情况:

```bash
CAR_COLOR: 车辆颜色
COVER_CARNUM: 遮污车牌
CAR_NUM_COLOR: 车牌颜色
CAR_TYPE: 车辆类型
CAR_NUM_TYPE: 车牌类型
CAR_LOGO_TYPE: 车辆品牌
```

**以车辆颜色的请求示例.**

POST请求URL: `http://{{ip}}:{{port}}/goSearch/query.htm`

JSON类型的请求体:

```json
{
	"requestHeader": {
		"serviceType": 2,
		"requestType": 5
	},
	"request": {
		"algorithm": {
			"condition": {
				"algorithmType": "analyzeByProperty",
				"tableName": "c_picrecord",
				"beginTime": "2019-10-05 10:00:00",
				"property": "CAR_COLOR",
				"endTime": "2019-11-05 10:00:00",
```

# 4  GoSearch-ES 华为认证版本

## 4.1  String 条件查询

POST请求URL: `http://{{ip}}:{{port}}/goSearch/query.htm`

JSON类型的请求体:

```json
{
	"requestHeader": {
		"serviceType": 2,
		"moduleType": 8,
		"requestType": 3
	}, 
	"request": {
		"natived": "{
			\"index\": \"tb_face\",
			\"condition\": {
				\"query\": {
					\"match_phrase\": { \"FaceID\": '44010000001190000001022019080610265800001' }
				},
				\"size\": 20
			}
		}"
	}
}
```



## 4.2  JSON 条件查询

POST请求URL: `http://{{ip}}:{{port}}/goSearch/query.htm`

JSON类型的请求体:

```json
{
	"requestHeader": {
		"serviceType": 2,
		"moduleType": 8,
		"requestType": 3
	},
	"request": {
		"natived": {
			"index": "tb_motor_vehicle",
			"condition": {
				"size": 1,
				"query": {
					"match_all": { }
				}
			}
		}
	}
}
```
